      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "If the world is relentlessly demanding, maybe the most radical act you can take is to give yourself permission to demand nothing from yourself right now. That feeling of drifting, of being a ghost, is a sign that your energy reserves are completely depleted. If the weight feels unbearable, please know that there are people who want to help you carry it, so reach out to a crisis hotline immediately.",
